metadata.description:
ORIGINAL NFT 1/1

This is the first release of the series MONKEY SEE - MONKEY DOUG. from the newly created CRYPTO-DOUG stable.

This limited edition release drop is exclusively available through Lloyds Auctions.

About the Artist:

Australian artists Nick Morris and David Bowers launch their second series of NFT's. MONKEY SEE- MONKEY DOUG. Morris and Bowers were the first Australian artists to ever release a series of NFTs on an Australian platform and this is their second release.
Bowers and Morris create artwork collaboratively under the name 'Doug Bartlett' and have achieved national and international acclaim for their work. They were finalists in the 2010 Moran portraiture prize, have provided album cover art for the Hoodoo Gurus and T-shirt art for iconic art/fashion label Mambo.
